# append(contentsOf:)

**Instance Method**

Adds the contents of a PencilKit drawing on top of this paper.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(contentsOf drawing: PKDrawing)
```

## Parameters

- **drawing**: The drawing whose contents is added on top of this paper.
